<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>RAM CEU DAWH CH477</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ni khatkhat cu Pa-ra-dise ram tlangdawh lei cu kan hei cuan tawn, Ni
 khatkhat cu kan lung chungah, Pangpar rimhmui bangin aa zel, Ni khatkhat
 cu ka lung chungah liam cia caan an hung chuak ve tawn, Ni khatkhat cu
 kan lung chungah liamcia caan an hung chuak ve tawn, Dawtmi hna he zatial
 tlaih in, Ram ceu dawh ah kan leng ti lai, Ram ceu dawh ah kan leng ti
 lai, Zatial tlaih in kan leng ti lai, Ram ceu dawh ah hmunkhat te ah, Ram
 ceu dawh ah, ram ceu dawh ah.

[V2]
 Ni khatkhat cu kan hnathlam ah sual teinak hla a hung cuang tawn, Ni
 khatkhat cu kan lung chungah, Philh khawh lomi a hung chuak tawn, Ni
 khatkhat cu hi thil vialte, dimhnak hmun ah kan hmuh te lai, Ni khatkhat
 cu hi thil vialte, dinhnak hmun ah kan hmuh te lai, dinhnak hmun ah kan
 hmuh te lai, Maw hawi le hna hngak ko rih u, Khi caan tha a phanh lai kan
 hngalh, Khi caan tha a phanh lai kan hngalh, Maw hawidawt hna hngak ko
 rih u, Khi caantha a phanh lai kan hngalh, Ram ceu dawh ah, ram ceu dawh
 ah.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
